I'd rather be, they fill in a, I'd rather be golfing, I'd rather be flying, I'd rather

00:46:59.379 --> 00:47:01.139
be.

00:47:01.139 --> 00:47:07.699
The songwriter said, give me a passion for souls, dear Lord.

00:47:07.699 --> 00:47:11.019
He longed to be preaching the gospel.

00:47:11.019 --> 00:47:12.179
Why?

00:47:12.179 --> 00:47:16.719
Because men are dying and they need Jesus.

00:47:16.719 --> 00:47:19.699
We have what they need.

00:47:19.699 --> 00:47:20.699
Amen?

00:47:20.699 --> 00:47:22.339
Go and tell.

00:47:22.339 --> 00:47:24.739
Lord, we love you.

00:47:24.739 --> 00:47:25.979
We thank you for loving us.

00:47:25.979 --> 00:47:29.579
We thank you for your word.

00:47:29.579 --> 00:47:35.539
Thank you for this Old Testament passage and Lord, the truth of the passage, but also the

00:47:35.539 --> 00:47:38.179
way that we can make application.

00:47:38.179 --> 00:47:54.999
Lord would you help us to take these moments and to truly do some self-examination.

00:47:54.999 --> 00:47:59.339
Help us Lord to be honest with you.

00:47:59.339 --> 00:48:03.739
Help us Lord to make decisions that would endure, would last.

00:48:03.739 --> 00:48:06.699
Decisions that would have some feet to them.

00:48:07.219 --> 00:48:17.979
Lord, if there's one here that's not saved, they do not know with 100% confidence that

00:48:17.979 --> 00:48:19.539
heaven is their home.

00:48:19.539 --> 00:48:23.899
If that's you this morning and you say, I just don't know preacher, I don't know if

00:48:23.899 --> 00:48:29.419
I were to die that I'd go to heaven, but I'd like to know.

00:48:29.419 --> 00:48:33.719
I don't want to go through life without knowing.

00:48:33.719 --> 00:48:37.639
If that's you this morning, we have some folks here that will take a Bible and show

00:48:37.639 --> 00:48:39.599
you how you can know for sure that heaven's your home.

00:48:39.599 --> 00:48:42.159
If you're a man, Brother Mark will meet with you.

00:48:42.159 --> 00:48:46.599
If you're a lady, Brianna will meet with you and take a Bible and show you how you can

00:48:46.599 --> 00:48:48.639
know for sure that heaven's your home.

00:48:48.639 --> 00:48:51.919
Oh, we would not want you to leave here without knowing that.

00:48:51.919 --> 00:48:56.759
But if you're saved this morning, would you make the decision to be active in sowing the

00:48:56.759 --> 00:48:58.319
seed?

00:48:58.319 --> 00:49:02.479
Lord, would you have your will and way for it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:49:02.479 --> 00:49:04.239
Would you stand with me?

00:49:04.239 --> 00:49:07.799
Kimberly's going to play quietly on the piano and as she does, the altar is open.

00:49:07.799 --> 00:49:10.399
If you're not sure of heaven, would you come and take a Bible and show you how you can

00:49:10.399 --> 00:49:13.119
know for sure that heaven's your home?

00:49:13.119 --> 00:49:16.439
If you're saved this morning, how are you going to respond?

00:49:16.439 --> 00:49:18.999
Go and tell as Kimberly plays, the altar is open.

